Package: ccswresp
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: uhozicloud <uhouzicloud@github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/uhozicloud/ccswresp
Description: Protocol translation proxy: OpenAI Responses API ↔ Chat Completions API
 ccswresp is a local protocol translation proxy that converts OpenAI Responses
 API requests to Chat Completions API format and vice versa. It enables Codex
 CLI to work with any LLM backend that provides a Chat Completions API
 (DeepSeek, OpenAI, etc.).
 .
 No runtime dependencies — it's a single static Go binary.
